Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Spray one eight-inch square pan with baking spray. Set aside Mix crust ingredients together in a mixing bowl. Mix well. Press into prepared pan. Bake 8 minutes or until firm. Mix cream cheese and SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener together until smooth. Add eggs, one at a time, mixing well after each addition. Add vanilla, mint extract and green food coloring; mix well. Pour over prepared crust. Bake in preheated oven for 30 minutes, or until firm. Refrigerate cheesecake bars 2 hours or until chilled and firm. Melt chocolate and drizzle over the top.